<div class="title">Against the Advices</div>
<div class="substance">Hydromorphone (Dilaudid) & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=-Westmount-&Exact=1">-Westmount-</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; -Westmount-. "Against the Advices: An Experience with Hydromorphone (Dilaudid) & Alcohol (exp75657)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 19, 2009. erowid.org/exp/75657</div>

<br/>



